{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_01_05_02",
  "title": "ジャック\nポット！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "あはははっ、いや～、大成功、大成功！\nもう最っ高な気分だわ～！　ラスベガス大好き！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahaha‚ yeah~‚ what a huge success‚ a huge success!\nI feel amazing~! I love Las Vegas!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 10.5419050217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.7685756989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "てか山田さん、さっきあのプロモーターが\nなんて言ったか聞いてた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Yamada-san‚ did you hear\nwhat that promoter said?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7685756989,
      "endTime": 15.9117730446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.1029068616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "あー、ごめん。英語出来ないんだっけ。kanaが\n中一の時使ってた教科書、貸してあげようか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~‚ sorry. You can’t speak English‚ can you? Should kana\nlend you the textbook I used in seventh grade?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1029068616,
      "endTime": 24.322294679000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.513428496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "こ、このクソガキ……あんたのはしゃぎ様から\n大体なんて言ってたかくらい想像出来るわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you little brat… I can pretty much imagine\nwhat he said from your giddy reaction!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.513428496,
      "endTime": 32.4393239961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6304578133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "『日本のトップアイドルの実力を見せてもらった\nとても素晴らしかったわ』……と、言っていたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I witnessed the talent of Japan’s top idols.\nIt was truly magnificent.\"……That's what he said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6304578133,
      "endTime": 39.8039996452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、まぁ当然の反応かしら\n私達の実力を世界に見せつけられたってことね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph‚ well‚ that's a natural reaction‚ I suppose.\nIt means we’ve shown the world our true potential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9951334623,
      "endTime": 48.3065851835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.4977190005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あの人にはサクラの手配を頼んだのだから\nハッタリなのも当然、知っているはずなのだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we asked him to arrange the shills‚\nso he must know it was all a bluff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4977190005,
      "endTime": 55.6758441912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8669780083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "それだけkana達のショーが凄かったってことよ\nふはははははは、勝った！　大勝利！　ザマァ見ろ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That just means our show was that amazing.\nFuhahahahahaha‚ we won! A landslide victory! Take that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8669780083,
      "endTime": 64.6162301369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.8073639539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そうね。『帰国前に今度はもう少し豪華な\nショーに出てみないか』って話をもらえたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ you’re right. He even asked‚ “Before you go back to Japan‚\nwould you be interested in performing in a more extravagant show?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8073639539,
      "endTime": 72.1770932821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3682270991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "遅いっつーの！　あいつがもっと早くkana達の実力\nを知ってれば今日のステージも豪華だったのに～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Too late~! If he’d known about our talent sooner‚\ntoday’s stage would’ve been more glamorous~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3682270991,
      "endTime": 80.22067584860001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4118096657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "……でもなんだか、本当に\n海外でも活動出来るんじゃないかって気がしてきたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But somehow‚ I’m starting to think\nthat we could actually make it overseas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4118096657,
      "endTime": 86.13437178800001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　……そ、その場合でも\nその、星見プロとの契約も残していただけると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? …E-even in that case‚\nwould you… still stay under contract with Hoshimi Pro…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.325505605,
      "endTime": 93.8917643216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.0828981386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "うわ、めっちゃ慌ててるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Woah‚ he’s totally panicking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0828981386,
      "endTime": 97.1870930658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.3782268829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "んー、どうしましょうかねぇ\n基本給をアップしてくれるなら、交渉に応じますけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ what should we do?\nIf you increase our base salary‚ we’ll consider negotiating?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3782268829,
      "endTime": 105.2037596054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3948934224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "fran、冗談はそのへんにしておきなさい\n私達にはまだ日本でやるべきことがあるでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran‚ stop joking around.\nWe still have things to do in Japan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3948934224,
      "endTime": 112.34687239189999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……まずは、正真正銘\n日本のトップアイドルになるのが先ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right… First‚ we need to\ntruly become top idols from Japan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.538006209,
      "endTime": 119.28757543430001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.4787092514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "途中で海外に行ったら、逃げ出したとか思われそう\nそんな格好悪いの、まっぴらごめんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we go overseas in the middle of things‚ people will think we ran away.\nI absolutely refuse to look that pathetic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4787092514,
      "endTime": 127.28011496730001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――帰国後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After returning to Japan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2712487843,
      "endTime": 129.2712487843,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1445.2107450999847
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.2712487843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ。kanaって、ラスベガスでショーも成功させた\nすご～いアイドルのはずなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ kana is the amazing idol who made it big\neven in Las Vegas‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1712426808,
      "endTime": 137.8847348836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0758687006
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "なんで、次のスタジオまで電車移動なわけ？\nしかも、あんた達と一緒に歩かされるなんて最悪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "why am I taking the train to the next studio?\nAnd to top it all off‚ I have to walk with you guys. This is the worst.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0758687006,
      "endTime": 146.37650384769998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.5676376648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "文句を言いたいのはお互い様よ。はーあ……仕事場で\n顔を合わせてる時間さえもうんざりなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re not the only one who wants to complain. Sigh… I’m already\nsick of seeing your faces in the workplace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5676376648,
      "endTime": 155.3236923523,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13818.821862800007
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14088.821862799989
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "まぁいいや。kana、最近は凄く気分がいいし\n見て、kana達まだ海外で話題になってるっぽいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whatever. kana is in a really good mood lately‚\nand look‚ it seems like we’re still a hot topic overseas!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.5148261693,
      "endTime": 165.2148257878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.7831261943
    },
